  "remarks": "\nChairperson' of the 'Central Electoral Commission' of the so-called 'Luhansk People's Republic.' In this capacity, she participated in the organisation of the so-called 'elections' of 11 November 2018 in the so-called 'Luhansk People's Republic\", and thereby actively supported and implemented actions and policies which undermine the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine, and further destabilised Ukraine. The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
